OL,3,CArsonist who poured petrol over barber
OL,4,Cshop and set it alight jailed
OL,6,FCCTV footage from inside the
OL,7,Fbarbershop was shown to the court.
OL,9,FA man who poured petrol over a
OL,10,Fbarbershop before setting it alight
OL,11,Fhas been sentenced to more than seven
OL,12,Fyears in prison
OL,14,FDilovan Sindi, 39, caused an explosion
OL,15,Fat the premises in the Westerhope area
OL,16,Fof Newcastle on 23 May 2023 which
OL,17,Fresulted in both him and another man
OL,18,Fsuffering serious burn injuries.
