OL,3,CArsonist who poured petrol over barber
OL,4,Cshop and set it alight jailed
OL,6,FIt is believed Sindi was in dispute
OL,7,Fwith the owner of the business and was
OL,8,Flooking to target him.
OL,10,FCCTV pictures from inside the barber
OL,11,Fshop show Sindi entering the building,
OL,12,Fbefore pouring a can of petrol over
OL,13,Ffurniture in the shop.
OL,15,FA struggle followed but Sindi ignited
OL,16,Fthe fuel with a lighter.
