OL,3,CArsonist who poured petrol over barber
OL,4,Cshop and set it alight jailed
OL,6,FOne of the victims suffered 65 per
OL,7,Fcent burns to his body and was
OL,8,Fhospitalised for several months. He
OL,9,Fwas later discharged but continues to
OL,10,Fbe treated for his injuries.
OL,12,FA child and his father who were in the
OL,13,Fshop at the time were not physically
OL,14,Finjured, but both suffered serious
OL,15,Fpsychological effects from the attack.
OL,17,FOne man escaped without injury, while
OL,18,Fanother sustained minor injuries to
OL,19,Fhis leg and continues to receive
OL,20,Fcounselling as a result of the
OL,21,Fincident.
