OL,3,CArsonist who poured petrol over barber
OL,4,Cshop and set it alight jailed
OL,6,FSindi, of Sulgrave Road, Washington,
OL,7,Fsustained serious burns to his body in
OL,8,Fthe incident. After several months of
OL,9,Fhospital treatment, he was arrested
OL,10,Fand charged with three counts of
OL,11,Fattempted murder and one count of
OL,12,Farson with intent to endanger life.
OL,14,FIn September 2024, Sindi pleaded
OL,15,Fguilty to arson with intent to
OL,16,Fendanger life, grievous bodily harm
OL,17,Fand attempted wounding at Newcastle
OL,18,FCrown Court.
