OL,3,CArsonist who poured petrol over barber
OL,4,Cshop and set it alight jailed
OL,6,FHe was remanded in custody after the
OL,7,Fhearing until today (Wednesday 15
OL,8,FJanuary) when he was sentenced to
OL,9,Fseven years and two months in prison.
OL,11,FSpeaking after the hearing, Detective
OL,12,FInspector Rona Malessa, of Northumbria
OL,13,FPolice, said: "First and foremost we
OL,14,Fwould like to pay tribute to the
OL,15,Fvictims.
OL,17,F"They have been put through a
OL,18,Fhorrendous ordeal and we hope that
OL,19,Fthey can take some closure now that
OL,20,Ftheir attacker has been jailed.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
