OL,6,F"I would also like to thank our
OL,7,Fpartner organisations Tyne and Wear
OL,8,FFire and Rescue Service and the North
OL,9,FEast Ambulance Service who were so
OL,10,Fcrucial to the emergency response on
OL,11,Fthe day in putting out the blaze and
OL,12,Fgetting those injured the appropriate
OL,13,Ftreatment before transporting them to
OL,14,Fhospital.
