OL,3,CArsonist who poured petrol over barber
OL,4,Cshop and set it alight jailed
OL,6,F"Sindi's actions on May 23, 2023, were
OL,7,Futterly abhorrent and he caused
OL,8,Fserious, life-changing injuries to one
OL,9,Fof his victims. It is fortunate that
OL,10,Fwe are not dealing with much worse
OL,11,Foutcomes given the seriousness of the
OL,12,Fattack that day.
OL,14,F"I hope this case demonstrates to the
OL,15,Fpublic that we will always look to
OL,16,Fprosecute violent offenders in our
OL,17,Fcommunities and do everything we can
OL,18,Fto put them before the courts and
OL,19,Fbring them to justice."
